unique_row_id.name: unique_row_id
unique_row_id.comment: A unique identifier for the trip, generated by hashing key trip attributes.

filename.name: filename
filename.comment: The source filename from which the trip data was loaded.

VendorID.name: VendorID
VendorID.comment: A code indicating the LPEP provider that provided the record. 1= Creative Mobile Technologies, LLC; 2= VeriFone Inc.

tpep_pickup_datetime.name: tpep_pickup_datetime
tpep_pickup_datetime.comment: The date and time when the meter was engaged

tpep_dropoff_datetime.name: tpep_dropoff_datetime
tpep_dropoff_datetime.comment: The date and time when the meter was disengaged

passenger_count.name: passenger_count
passenger_count.comment: The number of passengers in the vehicle. This is a driver-entered value.

trip_distance.name: trip_distance
trip_distance.comment: The elapsed trip distance in miles reported by the taximeter.

RatecodeID.name: RatecodeID
RatecodeID.comment: The final rate code in effect at the end of the trip. 1= Standard rate 2=JFK 3=Newark 4=Nassau or Westchester 5=Negotiated fare 6=Group ride

store_and_fwd_flag.name: store_and_fwd_flag
store_and_fwd_flag.comment: This flag indicates whether the trip record was held in vehicle memory before sending to the vendor, aka "store and forward," because the vehicle did not have a connection to the server. TRUE = store and forward trip, FALSE = not a store and forward trip

PULocationID.name: PULocationID
PULocationID.comment: TLC Taxi Zone in which the taximeter was engaged

DOLocationID.name: DOLocationID
DOLocationID.comment: TLC Taxi Zone in which the taximeter was disengaged

payment_type.name: payment_type
payment_type.comment: A numeric code signifying how the passenger paid for the trip. 1= Credit card 2= Cash 3= No charge 4= Dispute 5= Unknown 6= Voided trip

fare_amount.name: fare_amount
fare_amount.comment: The time-and-distance fare calculated by the meter

extra.name: extra
extra.comment: Miscellaneous extras and surcharges. Currently, this only includes the $0.50 and $1 rush hour and overnight charges

mta_tax.name: mta_tax
mta_tax.comment: $0.50 MTA tax that is automatically triggered based on the metered rate in use

tip_amount.name: tip_amount
tip_amount.comment: Tip amount. This field is automatically populated for credit card tips. Cash tips are not included.

tolls_amount.name: tolls_amount
tolls_amount.comment: Total amount of all tolls paid in trip.

improvement_surcharge.name: improvement_surcharge
improvement_surcharge.comment: $0.30 improvement surcharge assessed on hailed trips at the flag drop. The improvement surcharge began being levied in 2015.

total_amount.name: total_amount
total_amount.comment: The total amount charged to passengers. Does not include cash tips.

congestion_surcharge.name: congestion_surcharge
congestion_surcharge.comment: Congestion surcharge applied to trips in congested zones

partitioning_type.label: Partitioned By
partitioning_type.description: The partitioning column for this table
